      <description>&lt;h4 id=&#34;disclaimer-image-is-generated-using-chatgpt&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DISCLAIMER:&lt;/strong&gt; Image is generated using &lt;code&gt;ChatGPT&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/h4&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;As you all know, I started working on my second book, tentatively titled, &lt;code&gt;&amp;quot;The Perl ORM Handbook: DBIx::Class&amp;quot;&lt;/code&gt; towards the end of &lt;code&gt;2025&lt;/code&gt;. With the start of the new year, my focus shifted to a related project: a CPAN module called, &lt;a href=&#34;https://metacpan.org/dist/DBIx-Class-Async&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DBIx::Class::Async&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. As you can imagine, that project took up bulk of my spare time. Now that it has settled down a bit, I am ready to return to the book&amp;rsquo;s manuscript.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
